<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
        <header class="mb-auto">
            <div>
                <h3 class="float-md-left mb-0">YelpCamp</h3>
                <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-right">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/campgrounds">Campgrounds</a>
                    <% if(!currentUser) { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                    <% } %>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="px-3">
            <h1>YelpCamp</h1>
            <p class="lead"> Welcome to YelpCamp! <br>Looking for the perfect getaway? Look no further than our camping site! Nestled in the heart of nature, our site offers a serene and relaxing environment that's perfect for families, couples, and solo travelers alike.
                At our camping site, you'll find everything you need for an unforgettable adventure. Whether you're a seasoned camper or a first-timer, our team is here to help you make the most of your stay. We offer a range of camping options to suit your needs, including tent sites, RV sites, and cabins.
                Our facilities are top-notch, too. You'll enjoy access to clean restrooms and showers, as well as laundry facilities and a camp store stocked with everything you need for your stay. And of course, there's plenty to do around our site, from hiking and fishing to birdwatching and stargazing.
                
                Ready to book your stay? Visit our website to learn more about our camping site and reserve your spot today. We can't wait to welcome you to our little slice of paradise!</p>
            <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold border-white bg-white">View
                Campgrounds</a>
        </main>

        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2023 </p>
        </footer>


    </div>


